<hw>Bow"er</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To embower; to inclose.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bower</ent>⟦br⟧

