<hw>Bow"er</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To lodge.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bower</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 6 ====
HEADWORD: Bower
<hw>Bow"er</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Bough</er>, cf.
<er>Brancher</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Falconry)</fld> <def>A young hawk, when
